          "type": "explanation",
          "name": "MIN/MAX SPAWN COUNTS",
          "definition": "When spawning a number of squads from this wave template, try and spawn at least the minimum number, and at most the maximum number. Once these min/max bounds have been met, probabilistic distribution will continue."
